                     <interp inst="t18360229-867-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>for stealing, on the <rs id="t18360229-cd-172" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18360229-867-offence-1 t18360229-cd-172"></join>9th of February</rs>, 64<hi rend="italic">lbs</hi>. weight of lead, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18360229-name-1292" type="victimName">
